    <article id="article-4" class="hn-article" data-index="4">
        <h1 class="title">
            <a href="https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2018-10-03/tesla-s-model-3-is-becoming-one-of-america-s-best-selling-sedans">
                Tesla’s Model 3 Is Becoming One of America’s Best-Selling Sedans
            </a>
        </h1>
        <p class="meta">
            <a href="https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2018-10-03/tesla-s-model-3-is-becoming-one-of-america-s-best-selling-sedans">www.bloomberg.com</a>
