<span class="h2"><a class="selflink" href="#appendix-A">Appendix A</a>.  Decoding Tables for Predefined Codes</span>

   This appendix contains FSE decoding tables for the predefined literal
   length, match length, and offset codes.  The tables have been
   constructed using the algorithm as given above in <a href="#section-4.1.1">Section 4.1.1</a>.  The
   tables here can be used as examples to crosscheck that an
   implementation has built its decoding tables correctly.

<span class="h3"><a class="selflink" href="#appendix-A.1">A.1</a>.  Literal Length Code Table</span>

     +-------+--------+----------------+------+
     | State | Symbol | Number_Of_Bits | Base |
     +-------+--------+----------------+------+
